text: @FedEx Why has my package been sitting for 48 hours in the same spot? A spot that is only 12 hours drive from my house?
@mrpigs @mrpigs: I'd like to help and get this resolved for you! Please send the tracking # and delivery address. Sonia

@FedExHelp There's no emergency. It's just every time I order from a company that uses Fedex it takes forever for package to arrive. In future I'll screen my ordering to companies that use different delivery method.
